{"tid":286594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人] 網上賣嘢嘅唔該入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-06-16T17:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T17:18:10.000Z","uid":62217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"057f27fafe3c47c6f42f87da1faddd735c2955c0","tid":286594,"uid":62217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"小妹頭先翻到屋企，爸爸話唔小心拆錯郵件。<br />\n<br />\n一睇入面係名牌來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見好似冇回郵地址 ，入面又有張咁嘅紙，想問下係唔係你嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果你見倒，請留低聯絡方法</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不過，如果你一個星期內見唔倒，小妹唯有就咁放翻入郵筒啦<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/011732_91e67cd31ecd8213c6bf72957231e095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F011732_91e67cd31ecd8213c6bf72957231e095.jpg&h=fef16caf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}